@startuml UC-AUD-01
left to right direction
actor "Auditor / Regulator" as Auditor
actor "AI Agent (evidence aggregator)" as AI_Agent
actor "Internal Audit Lead" as AuditLead
rectangle "iNB Audit Service" {
  usecase "Request Evidence Package" as UC_Request
  usecase "Aggregate Logs & Reports" as UC_Aggregate
  usecase "Manual Validation / Remediation" as UC_Remedy
}
Auditor --> UC_Request
UC_Request --> UC_Aggregate
AI_Agent --> UC_Aggregate
UC_Aggregate .> UC_Remedy : escalate if gaps
AuditLead --> UC_Remedy
UC_Remedy --> UC_Aggregate : provide missing items
@enduml
